&lt;li&gt;Configure and manage Azure networking components including:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Virtual Networks (VNets)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network Security Groups (NSGs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Load Balancers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;VPN Gateways&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private Endpoints&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and optimize Azure cloud costs using &lt;strong&gt;Azure Cost Management&lt;/strong&gt;, budgets, and resource optimization best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage &lt;strong&gt;Microsoft 365 (Office 365)&lt;/strong&gt; users, licenses, subscriptions, and administrative tasks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Administer Windows Server and Linux server environments, including installation, configuration, patching, and performance tuning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configure and manage &lt;strong&gt;Fortinet Firewalls&lt;/strong&gt;, including:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Firewall Policies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NAT Rules&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Site-to-Site &amp;amp; Remote Access VPNs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Security Policies&lt;/li&gt;
